Package org.project3.rest_api.models

Class Order

java.lang.Object
org.project3.rest_api.models.Order
public class Order extends Object
The Order class represents a customer order in the Panda Express POS system. It stores information about the order, including the order ID, cashier ID, date and time details, total price, and items purchased. The items are divided into two categories: inventory items and menu items.
Author:
Kevin Zhang, Soham Nagawanshi, Ryan Kha
